    "content": "18. 함수 $y = t \\cdot 2^x$ ($0 < t < 1$)의 그래프가 두 함수 $y = 2^{-x}$, $y = -2^x + 4$의 그래프와 만나는 점을 각각 P, Q라 하자.\\n점 P와 점 Q의 $x$좌표의 비가 $1:2$일 때, $t$의 값은? (4.6점)\\n<svg width=\"250\" height=\"200\" viewBox=\"0 0 250 200\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\\n  <line x1=\"20\" y1=\"140\" x2=\"230\" y2=\"140\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"1\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\\n  <line x1=\"80\" y1=\"180\" x2=\"80\" y2=\"40\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"1\" marker-end=\"url(#arrow)\"/>\\n  <text x=\"225\" y=\"155\" font-size=\"12px\">x</text>\\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"45\" font-size=\"12px\">y</text>\\n  <text x=\"70\" y=\"150\" font-size=\"12px\">O</text>\\n  <path d=\"M 40.0,80.0 L 42.86,82.9 L 45.71,85.66 L 48.57,88.28 L 51.43,90.78 L 54.29,93.16 L 57.14,95.42 L 60.0,97.57 L 62.86,99.62 L 65.71,101.57 L 68.57,103.43 L 71.43,105.2 L 74.29,106.88 L 77.14,108.48 L 80.0,110.0 L 82.86,111.45 L 85.71,112.83 L 88.57,114.14 L 91.43,115.39 L 94.29,116.58 L 97.14,117.71 L 100.0,118.79 L 102.86,119.81 L 105.71,120.79 L 108.57,121.71 L 111.43,122.6 L 114.29,123.44 L 117.14,124.24 L 120.0,125.0 L 122.86,125.72 L 125.71,126.41 L 128.57,127.07 L 131.43,127.69 L 134.29,128.29 L 137.14,128.86 L 140.0,129.39 L 142.86,129.91 L 145.71,130.39 L 148.57,130.86 L 151.43,131.3 L 154.29,131.72 L 157.14,132.12 L 160.0,132.5 L 162.86,132.86 L 165.71,133.21 L 168.57,133.54 L 171.43,133.85 L 174.29,134.14 L 177.14,134.43 L 180.0,134.7\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/>\\n  <path d=\"M 60.0,41.21 L 62.2,42.04 L 64.41,42.9 L 66.61,43.79 L 68.82,44.71 L 71.02,45.68 L 73.22,46.68 L 75.43,47.72 L 77.63,48.79 L 79.84,49.92 L 82.04,51.08 L 84.24,52.29 L 86.45,53.55 L 88.65,54.85 L 90.86,56.21 L 93.06,57.62 L 95.27,59.08 L 97.47,60.61 L 99.67,62.19 L 101.88,63.83 L 104.08,65.54 L 106.29,67.31 L 108.49,69.15 L 110.69,71.06 L 112.9,73.05 L 115.1,75.12 L 117.31,77.26 L 119.51,79.49 L 121.71,81.81 L 123.92,84.22 L 126.12,86.72 L 128.33,89.31 L 130.53,92.01 L 132.73,94.82 L 134.94,97.73 L 137.14,100.75 L 139.35,103.9 L 141.55,107.16 L 143.76,110.56 L 143.76,110.56 L 145.96,114.08 L 148.16,117.75 L 150.37,121.55 L 152.57,125.51 L 154.78,129.61 L 156.98,133.88 L 159.18,138.31 L 161.39,142.92 L 163.59,147.71 L 165.8,152.68 L 168.0,157.84\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/>\\n  <path d=\"M 48.0,134.26 L 50.69,133.98 L 53.39,133.69 L 56.08,133.39 L 58.78,133.08 L 61.47,132.75 L 64.16,132.4 L 66.86,132.04 L 69.55,131.66 L 72.24,131.26 L 74.94,130.84 L 77.63,130.4 L 80.33,129.94 L 83.02,129.46 L 85.71,128.96 L 88.41,128.43 L 91.1,127.88 L 93.8,127.3 L 96.49,126.69 L 99.18,126.06 L 101.88,125.39 L 104.57,124.69 L 107.27,123.96 L 109.96,123.19 L 112.65,122.39 L 115.35,121.55 L 118.04,120.67 L 120.73,119.74 L 123.43,118.78 L 126.12,117.76 L 128.82,116.7 L 131.51,115.59 L 134.2,114.42 L 136.9,113.2 L 139.59,111.92 L 142.29,110.57 L 144.98,109.17 L 147.67,107.69 L 150.37,106.15 L 153.06,104.53 L 155.76,102.84 L 158.45,101.06 L 161.14,99.2 L 163.84,97.25 L 166.53,95.21 L 169.22,93.07 L 171.92,90.82 L 174.61,88.47 L 177.31,86.01 L 180.0,83.43\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"black\" stroke-width=\"1.2\"/>\\n  <circle cx=\"111.7\" cy=\"122.7\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"black\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\\n  <text x=\"105\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"10px\">P</text>\\n  <circle cx=\"143.4\" cy=\"110.0\" r=\"2.5\" fill=\"black\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\\n  <text x=\"145\" y=\"105\" font-size=\"10px\">Q</text>\\n  <text x=\"35\" y=\"105\" font-size=\"10px\">y=2^{-x}</text>\\n  <text x=\"85\" y=\"60\" font-size=\"10px\">y=-2^x+4</text>\\n  <text x=\"175\" y=\"105\" font-size=\"10px\">y=t 2^x</text>\\n  <defs><marker id=\"arrow\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"10\" refX=\"0\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L6,3 z\" fill=\"black\"/></marker></defs>\\n</svg>",
